data.description: Charming 4 bedroom, 3 bath, two story Contemporary home in Rancho Del Lago. Primary suite has ensuite bath with large walk-in closets, spacious shower & separate tub. This stunning home boasts an inviting open floor plan, flooded with natural light. Entertain with ease in the open floor plan that flows seamlessly from the kitchen to the great room. The kitchen is a culinary haven, and counts with ample counter & storage space. Highly rated Vail School District. Convenient to I-10, Cienega High School, Raytheon, and much more. Come and take a look today!
